r"""
Interface to MuPAD

AUTHOR:
    -- William Stein 

You must have the optional commercial MuPAD interpreter installed and
available as the command \code{mupkern} in your PATH in order to use
this interface.  You do not have to install any optional \sage
packages.
"""

